Import Data to Power BI 11

 

Download and Load CSV File to Power BI Desktop





1. Open Power BI Desktop
2. Click on ‘Get data’ button.
3. Select Text/CSV and click on connect.
4. Select the 'electronics_data.csv' file ,click on Open and load after the preview displayed.

Follow the steps in the gif to import the table.
